item.description:
Your invited to say good bye to your boots and slip into your favorite pair of flip-flops as we kick off Spring at Michaels Harborside on Saturday, March 26th from  8-11PM.

Enter to win 2 Kenny Chesney tickets-Enjoy live music, sip summer cocktails and shuck Rawbar favorites.

Dinner is optional,  they have great food or just come to dance (you are responsible for your own bill).
